<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Information to help non-NHS bodies implement the NHS (Charges to Overseas Visitors) Regulations 2015, as amended. It signposts them to existing resources available to NHS bodies that will also be of use to non-NHS bodies.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

